    "Specifically, in the LIVE555 subject, CHATAFL increased the number of state transitions by 91% compared to AFLNET.",
    "Furthermore, CHATAFL explored the same number of state transitions 48× faster than AFLNET, on average.",
    "In comparison to NSFUZZ, CHATAFL covered 43% more state transitions on average and achieved the same number of state transitions 16× faster.",
